    <li>Ulcerative colitis. Patient brochure. 2012. Electronic copies: Available from the <a href="/web/20180712205352/https://www.guideline.gov/Home/Disclaimer?id=47756&amp;contentType=summary&amp;redirect=https%3a%2f%2fwww.fascrs.org%2fpatients%2fdisease-condition%2fulcerative-colitis" title="American Society of Colon and Rectal Surgeons (ASCRS) Web site">American Society of Colon and Rectal Surgeons (ASCRS) Web site</a>&nbsp;<img alt="External Web Site Policy" src="/web/20180712205352im_/https://www.guideline.gov/UI/images/icon_externallink.gif"/>. </li>
